{"tid":1474300,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中国準備毒啞你地","createTime":"2019-08-15T06:31:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T12:56:56.000Z","uid":257398,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"88db0e56a588874ef0f8ce62dc0d310a1bd366dc","tid":1474300,"uid":257398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:31:27.000Z","msg":"【中文課程改革1】DSE中文刪聆聽、說話　前線老師批「行回頭路」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/354111\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Fsns%2Farticle%2F354111&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdkbB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=52d75e1c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/354111</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一個語言對一個文化黎講幾咁重要希望大家知道<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">愛</span></span> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">爱</span></span> 唔難明<br />\n<br />\n聆聽同說話比我地想像中重要得多，<br />\n我地每日做緊既佔95%都係呢兩樣，毒撚另計<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聆聽卷可以訓練思維，諗下人地到底想表達啲咩<br />\n說話卷可以訓練理性討論，用有用既理據去支持自己<br />\n<br />\n再睇下最近支那人攻網絡鬧我地廢青，<br />\n淨係識: 你媽逼死廢青，咩屎咩屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就好明顯知道一個native language會造就到咩人出黎<br />\n<br />\n日日馬b講嘢又無理據<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>我地一定要守護廣東話！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n除咗要對抗垃圾政府垃圾教育局既垃圾政策<br />\n身處海外讀書、交流、工作，甚至移居既你地<br />\n都有能力可以宣揚廣東話出去！<br />\n<br />\n學一個語言最重要係有興趣，<br />\n點樣先令外人無啦啦對你語言有興趣？<br />\n我地最叻啲咩啊？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: orange;\">係粗口啊屌你老母</span></ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n用廣東話講粗口既風味無一個語言比得上，<br />\n個種完全表達到憤怒既用詞，<br />\n<br />\nshut up貼切得過收皮?<br />\nBitch貼切得過死八婆?<br />\nDork貼切得過on9仔？<br />\nAsshole同<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>錫春袋</strong></span>拍馬都比唔上！<br />\n<br />\n中国都有本事令其他國家既人要識幾句普通話<br />\n香港點解唔可以輸出我地文化精粹既廣東話？<br />\n<br />\n唔好再將自己本土語言放係第二、第三位置了！"},{"pid":"ad202dcfd295a7dfcd02e7a89c6a818696375759","tid":1474300,"uid":257398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:33:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"612409c11c51b816eed35c4bf7256b496a83ce9a","tid":1474300,"uid":257398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:33:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7bca093a8574d2231a26605887683cd78f0c85fa","tid":1474300,"uid":257398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:33:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"12f3437fe740e10a4ec8493d2d1bbe0e081a72ac","tid":1474300,"uid":257398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:33:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1529c7b2779e6a0feb69b8bdd3857c9731106b49","tid":1474300,"uid":257398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:34:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"11832b12660f38828fcae53fa469e4cd30f2655c","tid":1474300,"uid":257398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:34:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"71050a0a25f10c7424bcf115c281da4b4a922be3","tid":1474300,"uid":257398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:34:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d25832914f9395bb2f4af5412c75072f3b149976","tid":1474300,"uid":257398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:34:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9badcd58e01dc9bd323be8f8e1a8098c97d94d3d","tid":1474300,"uid":257398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:34:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e9050e89e3bf687a9a48a1e6d0785a97e98dced3","tid":1474300,"uid":49588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:36:08.000Z","msg":"廣東話對契丹支那滿洲狗來講，太難學"},{"pid":"7548942d7fbe41406e8ae1c39d0ae5f90e91bf67","tid":1474300,"uid":257398,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e9050e89e3bf687a9a48a1e6d0785a97e98dced3","tid":1474300,"uid":49588,"like":1,"disli